Package net.demilich.metastone.game.decks Description

Decks contains code to define a collection of cards for play.
See Also:
for more about the deck, a description of which cards and hero class a user wants to play with., for the in-game state of the deck, which behaves like a {@link net.demilich.metastone.game.cards.CardZone} instead of a {@link net.demilich.metastone.game.decks.Deck}.
